      <p>
       W hv frgttn t wlk lghtly, nd nstd mn th rth f ts ntrl rsrcs, clrct frsts, pllt rvrs nd lks nd cns, ltr th lndscp t ft r nds, mk th r drty nd th rn cdc nd th zn hld.
      </p>
