       D I by grnr prdcts? D I by  grnr cr? D I rcycl ll th stff I s?
      </p>
      <p>
       Wll, sr. Y cn d ll f ths thngs, nd thy r sfl. Bt vn bttr: lv  lf f lss, nd wlk lghtr.
       <br/>
