       </span>
       <br/>
       A lf f lss mns y cnsm lss, s fwr ntrl rsrcs, pllt lss, wn lss stff, cntrbt lss t grnhs mssns.
      </p>
      <p>
       Mnmlsm, th phlsphy f  lf f lss, s mr sstnbl bcs t ss lss, nd ths rcyclng sn’t s ncssry (thgh t’s stll mprtnt). It’s nt sstnbl t cntn t cnsm hg mnts f prdcts (n mttr hw grn thy r) r s ntrl rsrcs (n mttr hw rgnc).
      </p>
      Thr’s  lt t wrt bt hr, nd I’ll wrt mr ltr, bt  fw brf xmpls:
      <br/>
      <ul>
       <li>
        <strong>
         By lss stff
        </strong>
        . Byng  lt f prdcts s t th hrt f ths. Rd mr:
        <a href="http://mnmlist.com/why-less-stuff-is-better/">
         Why lss stff s bttr
