         Rthnkng ncssts
        </a>
        .
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Et lss
        </strong>
        . Amrcns s  grp t wy t mch. It’s nt jst bt th hg mnts f ntrl rsrcs tht g nt prdcng ll f tht fd, lthgh tht’s hg (rd bt th rnfrsts bng clrct t mk grzng rm fr McDnld’s bf cws, fr xmpl). It’s ls bt th hg wstfl rstrnts, frm McDnld’s t Chls t Ln Str, srvng rdcls mnts f ft nd slt nd sgr ldn fd (nd thrwng mch f t wy), whn w cld smply t t hm. It’s bt ll th pckgng tht gs nt ll r frzn nd prcssd fd. It’s bt th hlth prblms tht rs frm tng s mch nhlthy fd, nd th wstd rsrcs tht g nt crng fr ll r dssd ppl, t ft frm ll th tng.
       </li>
       <li>
        <strong>
         Et lss mt
        </strong>
        . Mt s nt sstnbl. Mst f th crps w grw g t fdng nmls rsd fr fd r dry r ggs. If w stppd tng s mch mt, w wld s fwr rsrcs nd cld fd mr ppl.
       </li>
