        </strong>
        . It’s nsn hw mch pckgng s sd n ll th prdcts w by. Unfrtntly, thr sn’t mch chc whn y wnt t by smthng. Chs prdcts wth lss pckgng whn y d hv  chc. I thnk th pblc dmndng lss pckgng wll gt mnfctrrs t chng ths wstfl prctc.
